---
title: Sichuan-Glazed Snapper with Chilli-Garlic Rice & Soy Greens
description: We’ve gone a little bit fancy on you with this snazzy snapper, coated in a mild Sichuan sauce and loaded with tasty umami flavours. Accompanied by crunchy greens and chilli-infused garlic rice, you won't believe you whipped up such a delight.
